<body class="body-support-page">
  <div class="support-page-container">

    <header>
      <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="play-at-seventh">
      <h2>Play at Seventh!</h2>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        Want to play a show with us? Contact one of our collective members who specializes in a genre that best fits your band (see list below). We book up to 3 months in advance, so we may ask you to reach out again later if your show date is further in the future.
      </p>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        Please only contact one booker at a time. If you don’t hear back from us, follow up after a week or try a more general genre booker. If we can’t book your show, it’s nothing personal! We’re a small team doing our best.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="local-band-roster">
      <h2>Local Band Roster</h2>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        Add your band to our list of local acts! Bookers can reference this roster when looking for bands to fill out a lineup.
      </p>
      <%= link_to 'Submit your band', new_band_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
    </section>

    <section class="volunteer-at-seventh">
      <h2>Volunteer at Seventh</h2>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        Seventh Circle is 100% volunteer-run! We have opportunities to work the door, run sound, maintain the show space, or help with behind-the-scenes organization.
      </p>
      <a href="https://discord.com/invite/8Ev6rBqfTA" class="btn btn-secondary">Join the volunteer Discord</a>
    </section>

    <section class="donate-membership">
      <h2>Donate or Purchase a Membership</h2>
      <p class="support-page-paragraph">
        Support Seventh Circle Music Collective by donating or purchasing a membership.
      </p>
    </section>

